  "body": "Currently we have a minimal viable sync algorithm. Need to establish what work is required to improve sync performance and reliability. e.g distribute requests across peers, more coordination between block propagation manager and sync strategy.\n\n### TODO\n\n* [x] Start from common ancestor instead of finalised epoch\n* [ ] Avoid selecting the same peer for subsequent batches if possible\n* [x] Apply reputation penalties to peers\n* [ ] Implement a smarter/more efficient approach to verifying contested batches\n* [ ] Request updated status from all peers when a sync finishes\n* [ ] More intelligent grouping of target chains in non-finalised period\n* [ ] Consider starting background sync of less popular chains after reaching head",
